<%= h2_with_anchor "Integration with LangChain Agents" %>

<p>The tool is designed to work seamlessly with LangChain agents:</p>

<%= h3_with_anchor "Agent Configuration" %>

<pre><code class="language-typescript">import { ChatOpenAI } from "@langchain/openai";
import { AgentExecutor } from "langchain/agents";
