<%= h3_with_anchor "Similarity Scoring" %>

<p>Results are ranked by cosine similarity between query and icon embeddings:</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>0.8 - 1.0:</strong> Excellent match - highly relevant</li>
    <li><strong>0.6 - 0.8:</strong> Good match - relevant</li>
    <li><strong>0.4 - 0.6:</strong> Fair match - somewhat relevant</li>
    <li><strong>&lt; 0.4:</strong> Poor match - limited relevance</li>
</ul>

<%= h2_with_anchor "Performance & Caching" %>

<%= h3_with_anchor "Caching Strategy" %>

<p>The tool implements intelligent caching to optimize performance:</p>

<ol>
    <li><strong>Query-level caching:</strong> Results cached for 24 hours by default</li>
    <li><strong>Embedding reuse:</strong> Icon embeddings are pre-computed and stored</li>
    <li><strong>Parallel execution:</strong> Multiple queries processed simultaneously</li>
</ol>

