<%= h2_with_anchor "Best Practices" %>

<ol>
    <li><strong>Be Specific:</strong> Use descriptive queries rather than generic terms</li>
    <li><strong>Batch Queries:</strong> Group related searches into single requests</li>
    <li><strong>Cache Wisely:</strong> Leverage caching for frequently used queries</li>
    <li><strong>Limit Results:</strong> Request only as many icons as needed</li>
    <li><strong>Test Queries:</strong> Verify icon relevance in development</li>
    <li><strong>Provide Context:</strong> Include use case or UI element type in queries</li>
</ol>

<div class="alert alert-info">
    <p><strong>Pro Tip:</strong> When building icon pickers or selection interfaces, combine this tool with visual preview to let users make the final selection from semantically relevant options.</p>
</div>